    "3,703 randomlyselected discussion posts made by Monash University students including 2,339 (63%) content-relevant posts and 1,364 (37%) contentirrelevant posts.",
    "Dataset is publicly available.",
    "-Evaluated four traditional ML models: SVM, Random Forests, Logistic regression, and Naïve Bayes and two DL models: Bi-LSTM and CNN-LSTM.",
    "-Text embeddings generated using the tool Bert-asservice.",
    "-Trained classifiers with two samples: original sample and balanced sample (along gender and first language)."
